title: Bridget to Terabithia with Jessica Knoll: Thursday, October 6th, 2022
description:
1. Tom Brady Hires a Divorce Lawyer After Gisele Bundchen Retains Her Own (PEOPLE) (23:38)
  2. Fat Joe says he won't change his name even though he's no longer fat (Page Six) (31:42)
  3. Survivors of 1994 killing that's now subject of Kim Kardashian's Spotify podcast say no one contacted them (Daily Mail) (34:55)
  4. Scammer Anna Delvey granted bail, if she can find a place to stay (Page Six) (39:04)
  5. Patreon's deals with top TikTokers fell far short of expectations, leaked documents show (Business Insider) (42:36)

- Real Housewives of Beverly Hills Recap (51:45)

- Real Housewives of Salt Lake City Recap (59:06)

- Interview with Jessica Knoll  (1:02:50)
